model.name: Ribbed Tank Top
model.disambiguatingDescription: An instant go-to for everyday styling. This timeless tank top has a sleek and sporty feel in stretch viscose knitted with a blend of thin and thick ribbing for a subtly elevated finish in a comfortable, contouring fit. A palladium LV Circle chain detail adds a chic contemporary signature to the crew neck.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Main Material : 54% Viscose, 27% Polyester, 18% Polyamide, 1% Elastane
  • White
  • Regular fit
  • Made in Italy
  • Do not wash
  • Do not bleach
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron at a maximum sole-plate temperature of 110°C
  • Mild professionnal dry cleaning in hydrocarbons
